languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up Fast Payment (FPX) saya tidak muncul selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: If your top-up from Fast Payment (FPX) hasn't reflected after 10 minutes, please wait a bit longer as the system is processing. Typically, it should reflect within 1-10 minutes. If it still hasn't appeared after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda dari Fast Payment (FPX) tidak muncul selepas 10 minit, sila tunggu sedikit lagi kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, ia akan muncul dalam 1-10 minit. Jika ia masih belum muncul selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan.
